
 Tuzbolin - Table soccer simulator featuring Andatuz, the Guadalinex mascot
 ==========================================================================

 .- Quick start:
   1 - Edit the config file 'default-conf.yml' with information about your wiimotes including number of avaliable devices and bluetooth addresses

   2 - Launch 'python tuzbolin.py'

   If you are experiencing bad performance in controller response, try tweaking the game desired fps on globals.py.

 .- Dependencies:
   Pygame
   Ode python bindings
   Cwiid python module
   Python-yaml

   See doc/depends for details
